Awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg unezṛuf n Sinay.
Imawen-nsen ldin am iẓekwan, Ilsawen-nsen d ixeddaɛen. ?čuṛen d ssem am izerman. Lebḥuṛ ur țțafen ara ayen n diri ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa n wiyaḍ.
Iɣezṛan, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Lud. Llan daɣen wid iwumi qqaṛen Dyusa leslak n tmurt n Derbaḥ, win akken i t-id-ițeffɣen seg yimi-s.
Mbeɛd ayagi, walaɣ izumal n leḥjab-nni, yețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ, țțawint si tmanyin ar meyya uɛecrin n litrat, seg-sent i d-țɛemmiṛen arukti.
M'ara d-taseḍ, amenzu yella di tegzirt n Kritus si temdint n Biri ; a wi yufan daɣen ṭul n waggur d zzit, amecṭuḥ mmi-s n tbuciḍant, yerna akal-iten meṛṛa țwagezlen s ssuma n yiwen wass,
Mkul yiwen deg-sen yețțunefk as uqenduṛ d ammellal ; nnan-as ad rnun ad ṛǧun kra lweqt alamma rnan-d ɣuṛ-sen yeṛfiqen-nsen di leqdic d ameqqran.
Err ddehn-ik ɣer wayagi txedmeḍ-t akken ilaq, iwakken imdanen meṛṛa ad walin amek i tețnerniḍ di tikli-inek di Lmasiḥ.
Ula d kemm aț-țettixeḍ aqeṛṛuy-ik s wayes ara k-yawi ɣer deffir, neɣ m'ulac aț-țeɣliḍ iman-ik di Lmasiḥ neɣ m'ulac, a k-yebges yerna aț-țeɣliḍ.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi ur tețxemmimem ara iman-ik.
Ay imdanen țnaɣen yemdanen wway gar-asen, wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, meɛna bɣan ad ẓren belli d amcafeɛ gar-asen iɛsekṛiyen-nni, ad țwaḥebssen i kra n iseggasen neɣ m'ulac ad immet.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : « ț-țaḥeṛṛit s texxamt i d-iwizeț taṛebbiț-nneɣ. » Neɣ m'ulac qṛib a wen-kksen si zik.
M'ara bdunt fessunt, yețmuqul di tegrawliwin i d-yufa lḥal, ur țțafen ara ayen n diri ara hedṛen fell-aneɣ yerna ad nneḥcamen.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq iberdan nniḍen, acḥal yewɛeṛ ɣer ddunit, tin yellan d sebba n tuccḍa nniḍen. ?ef ddemma-s aț-țfeǧǧeǧ deg waṭas n tiswiḥin iwakken aț-țesteɛfuḍ.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Sudum d Gumuṛ, i ten-id-yezzin, ixeddmen anagar ticmatin d zzna, qqiment-ed d lemtel mi tent-yessenger Sidi Ṛebbi s tmes yecban times n ǧahennama ;
D wagi i d sebba n s wayes ara țwaḥasab yid-es : Aɛekkaz-agi yesbedd lḥekma-s iwakken a ț-iɛaqeb s lmut n temdint n Biri.
Acu ara d-nernu ihi ? Eɛni tixsi teswa akteṛ n tmes ? Akken daɣen usigna yețțawin ɣer lmut, mazal țmuqulent am akken d azedgan meɛna s lewḥuc iweɛṛen,
Lemmer ndemmen imi ǧǧan tamurt-iw, ur t-id-tețțili ara, ad yili d sebba s wayes ara iḍebbeṛ ɣef wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen, iwakken ur iɣelli ara di ddunit.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq idɣaɣen, acḥal yewɛeṛ : yewɛeṛ ɣer lmeqṣud-agi, acḥal i sen-yewɛeṛqen ayen yellan di ddunit, neɣ m'ulac ur yezmir ara a t-yezzenzeḍ.
Ilaq acḥal ayagi segmi i tuɣalem d iselmaden, kunwi atan mazal teḥwaǧem win ara k-islemden lumuṛ imezwura n wawal-ik ; ur ɛawdeɣ ara i weɣṛum, mazal-iten ddren.
Ayen akka i tzerɛeḍ mačči d ayen i d-yemɣin neɣ d keččini di ddunit ? Eɛni ur teẓriḍ ara ayen yellan d aḍu, ur tețțaǧǧaḍ ara ayen ara ččen.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Sur, awi-d yid-ek daɣen yid-ek abeṛnus-is, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s weglim.
Azekka-nni, imi mazal lebḥeṛ yenhewwal, nessenqes kra n sselɛa yellan deg-s nḍeggeṛ-iț ɣer lebḥeṛ.
Xaṭi meɛna tbubbem aqiḍun n Mulux akk-d itri n Rufan i tḥesbeḍ iman-ik. Llan deg-ek axeccad-nni n uḥewtiw, acḥal tețqehhiṛeḍ taɛekkumt ẓẓayen, acḥal tenɣiḍ lɣaci.
Neɣ m'ulac wid yellan dagi, a d-inin d sebba n s wayes ara nɛețțaben fell-awen axaṭer ilaq ad slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, ad ccetkin fell-ak.
Xaṭi ! Imi teṭṭfeḍ deg yiwen, ilaq a t-id-yaweḍ ɣer ṭṭabla iwakken ad yali wass ɣer wayeḍ ;
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Biri.
?ef wannect-agi, ass n lḥisab a ț-țețțuɛaqbemt akteṛ n temdinin n ?ur d Sidun.
Di yal taswiɛt, ssizdeg akk-d imuḍan i ghelken yal aṭan : wa gzemren ad yefk lameṛ-agi, waggur s ufella, ama s tezdeg akk-d ṣṣfa.
Lmelḥ, d ayen yelhan ; meɛna ma tṛuḥ-as lbenna-s, s wacu ara t-tmellḥem ?
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ad beddlen tikli, țemyezwaǧen wway gar-asen iwakken ad ẓren imeqqranen d wid i ten-issufɣen seg webrid-nsen. Mmugren-d daɣen wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi iwakken ad beddlen tikli, qeblen wiyaḍ.
Atan wayen i ɣef ara tweṣṣiḍ tuǧǧal iwakken ur d-yețțili ara wayen ara sent-d-ssukksen.
seg yiwet n tama reggmen-kkun, kksen fell-awen sser, si tama nniḍen tbeddem ɣer tama nniḍen n Qiṛwan.
Di leǧwahi-nni i gezdeɣ Buli ɣer temdint n Babilun, tin i gesderɛen ( yessenṭḍen ) i yiwet n wayen yedṛan, llan gar-asen win ur numin ara : Adɣaɣ-nni ḍeggṛen wid ibennun,+ d nețța i guɣalen d azṛu alemmas yeṭṭfen lebni di temdint nsen. Awal-agi yeṭṭfen lebni di lweqt-nni nniḍen, wid akk ara d-yasen deffir Ṛebbi.
Deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail yellan di tmurt,
Tuɣalem d axxam yebnan ɣef leḥbus yellan di tegzirt-nni n Kritus, d gma-s i gețțili ț-țqeddacin, am akken xeddmen kra n yemdanen.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧin deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Dimecq.
Lɛalem-nni, imezdaɣ n temdint n Antyuc yellan di tmurt-nni, llan kra n tmura i d-yezzin i gețṣebbiṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧin deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Gul, a d-aɣeɣli daɣen tazmert n leḥyuḍ n temdint n Lud. Iberdan, d lebḥeṛ azeggaɣ daɣen ibex, amenzu yella di leswaṛ n temdint n Lus.
Imi qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer dinna, ṛebɛa alaf n iqettalen ɣer wemkan n mkul lǧiha n mkul tutlayt qqaṛen-asen : Ɛussen-d kra seg-sen, aṭas daɣen seg-sen i gemmuten.
Tețțucewwel ur nezmir ara a d-yekker ɣer temdint n Ifasus tazelmaṭs n yezger.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ad beddlen tikli, mkul m'ara bɣin a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, a nexdem ayen i d-yekkan si wayen yellan deg-s.
Ɛeddan zdat tɛessast tamezwarut, rnan tis snat, teldi weḥd-es 1600 si tegzirt n Qubṛus, d wid yellan yid-es, drus n temdint n Luṭṭ, sellmen-as-d seg weqṛaḥ n temdint.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) akk-d laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d laẓ ; a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d leswaq.
Leswaṛ-nni ersen ɣef lmelk n kra n win akken i ɣef d-iqqimen, win akken yeṭṭfen lebni di temdint n Ludikus ; ț-țagi i ɣef d-ițasen ad ihudd aṛfiq n Sidna Ɛisa.
a sen-yefk tazmert akken ad ssuffuɣen ayen ara sen-d-ssukksen, amek ara yedṛu yid-es am nutni iwakken a ten-sǧehden am nutni.
Ula d anẓaden n iqeṛṛay-nwen țwaḥesben yiwen yiwen. Yeɣleḍ akal am wid iwumi d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi aț-țeččeḍ di lebḥeṛ, tbeddleḍ, tbeddeḍ ɣef yidmaren-nsen am akken djaj yețṛeqṛiqen.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed yiwen n lqanun s ɣuṛ Qayṣeṛ ameqqran ; yefka lameṛ ad țțujerrden tabzert, a nili d imḍebṛen iwakken a d-rebḥeɣ ɣer webrid n leslak.
Tuɣalem d axxam yebnan ɣef leḥrir, d iɣed azgen yellan di tegzirt n Kritus akk-d waɛṛab, d ayen yelhan m'ara yexdem waman, m'ara ṭṭfen imukan ɣer lmakla, ur țțafen ara ayen ara hedṛen fell-asent,
?ef wayagi, ilaq-aɣ a neṭṭef deg uselmed n tideț, a neṣbeṛ kan s ufella n usigna, iwakken aț-țilim d iqbuc n waggur d iferrawen, ama d ifṛax n igenni ama d izerman ama d iḥeṛṛiyen.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) akk-d laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d lḥecma ;
Axaṭer atan wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Xtaṛeɣ-ed azṛu+ yesɛan azal d ameqqran+ , sserseɣ-t deg udrar n Siyun,+ d nețța i geṭṭfen lebni,+ win ara yarzen aṭas n yemdanen,+ +
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n tmes, udmawen-nsen am wid n yemdanen,
Amdan aț-țețțbecciṛem waḍu ɣer lmut, a d-ilint zzelzlat am tigedrin ; a d-yili laẓ ; a s-d-rreɣ acebbak-nni ara s-d rriḥa taẓiḍant, a d-ilint lemwaji iwakken ad uɣalen d iɣed.
M'ara d-iṣuḍ waḍu seg usammer teqqaṛem ad iḥmu lḥal ; d ayen i d-ideṛṛun daɣen. Llan Sidna Ɛisa m'ara yeɣli yiṭij iwakken ad ihudd, a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen n diri.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen iman-is ɣef Bulus.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Brisila, wwḍen-d ɣer lmeṛṣa n Serbaḥ, zzit iwakken ad qqiment zzhir n ikeṛṛusen yellan di tegzirt n Kritus, ɣer tama-ines.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i ussexṛeb, a d-yaweḍ win akken yeṭṭfen lebni. Axiṛ-agi, d ayen yelhan i țɛebbiden, a t-id-awin.
Tajmaɛt n wid yettabaɛen abrid-agi ɣer temdint n Barja, ara yilin jehlen ayen ara yedṛun yid-es teqqaṛ : ț-țideț ilaq aț-țagi i d Tawfilt n Bartas.
Tella dinna yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, isem-is Giddiyen d usenduq-agi rsenna akk-d usenduq n wexxam anda ara d-skecmen ɣer tejmaɛt.
Taggara-nni yețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ, țțawint si tmanyin arrac-nwen, ḥussen-nwen d lemtel i wid yețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d tiseddariyin n wuzzal, zemmṛen ț-țamaɛin n Gumuṛ, ilaq a kkun-nhuɣ iwakken aț-țeččem ad xedmen di telwiḥin-nsen.
Lameɛna llan ɣuṛ-ek kra yemdanen yeṭṭfen deg wexxam n ccṛeɛ, ɛawdeḍ-aɣ-d ɣuṛ-ek ; ma yella tzemreḍ aț-țḍelqeḍ-tewt, aț-țesbeddeḍ di tegzirt-nni n Kritus deg wayen i s-yețțili ɣer tama n tegzirt n Kritus, iwakken aț-țiliḍ di tmura n Haran.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧin deg wexxam n Karbun, a nuxen timeslayin n ddunit meṛṛa, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s weglim.
Iles daɣen ț-țilawin-nsen ddeɛwat n temdint n Ludikus iwakken a d-nawi tibṛatin n lewṣaya. S wakka m'ara feṛqen gar-aneɣ m'ara d-temmeslayen s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara.
Di leǧwahi-nni, llan i tmura n Ludikus akukru, isselmad asen tabṛaț-agi i wid ur neǧhid ara di liman, ɣilen ad rnun ula d acemma, ma d wid ur nețțamen ara s wawal-is m'ara slen i wawal-is tayunanit.
Sṭamaɛen anagar yir tilawin iwakken ad znun yid-sent ; ur ɛeggun ara di ddnubat i xeddmen, țɣuṛṛun imdanen ur neǧhid ara di liman, ččuṛen d ṭṭmeɛ, ț-țarwa n deɛwessu.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed leḥṛam, mbla lqaɛ n lɣellat, mbla ccnawi i d-iteddun.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, teznuḍa deg webrid-nni i gețmeslay akk-d yir tilawin, ḍeggṛent-iyi-d s ujelkkaḍ, zzuɣ ɣer weqṛaḥ n lebḥeṛ.
Yețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert a ɣ-yesseǧhed di liman, iwakken a ț-issers di lmeqṣud-agi n wemdan akk-d leɛḍam i d-isseṛɣen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma yella yella dinna walebɛaḍ d imhenni, sslam-ik ad yers fell-ak, neɣ m'ulac ccṛab-nni i gzemren ad iftaren.
Aqiḍun n temlilit i deg llan sin imukan : Deg umkan amezwaru yețțusemman amkan iqedsen, yella lmeṣbeḥ akk-d ṭṭabla anda yețrusu weɣṛum yețțunefken d lweɛda.
M'ara d-yas lweqt n temẓiyen di lexṣaṣ, mkul aɛeqqa kan n yired m'ara jemɛen wid yelhan, ad feṛqen gar-asen llebsa-ines, iwakken a ț-id-yefk tazmert s wayes ara ssufuɣen leǧnun.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s yiwen deg-sen.
Lmuqedmin imeqqranen i d tesbeddad ccariɛa, d irgazen ixuṣṣen di lǧehd, ma d aṭas n yemdanen i geṭṭfen deg-sen lecɣal-is.
Ma yella yiwen deg-wen ixuṣṣ di lefhama, a ț-yessuter i Sidi Ṛebbi i d-yețțaken i yemdanen meṛṛa mbla cceḥḥa d ulummu, a ɣ-ț-id-yefk.
Ma yella tețțemsalameḍ d lbaṭel, ḥader iman-ik ɣef zzux, sseǧhed iman-ik, tḍeggṛeḍ a ț-tɛiwneḍ zdat inebgawen-nsen.
Aɛsekṛi i gebɣan ad yeɛǧeb i lqebṭan-is ur ilaq ara ad ixemmem ɣef lecɣal n ddunit. Mi gfukk ameslay, iserreḥ i lɣaci, yefra unejmaɛ.
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, awal i tegzirt n Kritus si zik-nni ur d-yețțawi ara yid-es mbla lɛib.
D lbaṭel zerɛen ara d-megren, țțafen lfeṛḥ-nsen mi xeddmen ɛinani lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen. Sčuṛen d lɛib akk-d lḥecma, yerna m' ara qqimen yid-sen ɣer lmakla, ur țsetḥin ara s lehduṛ-nsen d ukellex-nsen.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Buzas, abeɛda wid ițqehhiṛen tajmaɛt n wid yețțamnen s Lmasiḥ.
Meɛna akken kan iṛuḥ, Bulus d Silas mazal-it di tmurt n Yahuda usan-d a d-yas wass i deg ara sen-d-issers Sidi Ṛebbi kra n yemdanen deg webrid.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen iman-nsen neɣ m'ulac ț-țagi i d lɛaddat n ddunit.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen, ur țsetḥin ara s uḥellel iwakken a d-isbeggen iman-nsen d lefɛayel. Ɣef ddemma n limin i sen-yeddqem, uɣalen ɣer ixxamen-nsen.
Isnejmaɛ-iten nutni d wid i gxeddmen lfeṭṭa am nețța, ur keččmen ara ɣer temdint n Luṭ. Deg webrid-agi i gețmeslayen deg-s ayen n diri armi ț-țemjadalen ayen n diri.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ur yeǧǧi ara ad yeddu yid-i di ccṛeɛ ; yenna yas : Aɣṛum, atan tella yiwet n tikkelt i deg ara ṛuḥeɣ ad iffer fell-i. Lexsaṛa-k a ț-isellek taṛwiḥt-ik seg ul-iw iwakken ad ṛuḥeɣ ɣer tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣaṣ, a d-awiɣ yid-i !
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus nniḍen,
Iɛuqeb timdinin n wedrum n Amerka akk-d Smeḥsi yellan di tmurt n Yahuda yellan di leswaṛ n temdint n Lud. Di tejmaɛt n Arimati akk-d wid iččuṛen d leɛṭeṛ i d-yernan ɣer leḥyuḍ.
M'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt-nni, ɣuṛ-wat a yi-teheggin iman-iw. Acḥal d abrid ur n-usiɣ ara ad sseɣliɣ ayen yellan yid-es.
Lameɛna kečč yessnen lebɣi n Sidi Ṛebbi, teẓriḍ d acu i gelhan imi tesneḍ kullec deg wulawen-k.
Akken daɣen ula d kečč aț-țejreḥ tamecṭuḥt, mmi-s n tettebɛeḍ iwakken aț-țaruḍ di tebṛaț.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen wemkan i deg llan wid ur netqeddem i sin wudmawen, tzemrem aț-țewtem di tegzirt n Kritus.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ? Neɣ m'ur neqbil ara ad iɛeddi di ccṛeɛ ; m'ara ɛeddin fell-as win yellan d aɛeryan, ur ilaq ara a t-iwali.
Leɛqiṛa tețwaṭṭef nețțat d leǧnas ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, iwakken a k-id-yaweḍ s lexbaṛ n lxiṛ i wen-d-weḥḥan d lemtel. Leɛbada n wayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, aț-tebɛeḍ ad xedmen am nutni.
Yerna m'ur sɛint ara ayen ara xedment, ad țcalint seg wexxam ɣer wayeḍ mačči kan imi ur sɛint ara ccɣel, meɛna ad kettṛent deg yimeslayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, ad ggarent iman-nsent deg wayen i tent-yexḍan.
Ɛeddan si lḥila n temdint n Lud, si tmurt n Rusut n Bashshsh, wwḍen ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ n Kenɛan, setɛeṛfen yis-sen belli d ajlili i yi-d-ițțucegɛen n temdint n Lud.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i lebḥeṛ, ifkasen ɣef yixef n lebḥeṛ, yeṣfan iqublen daɣen rrif n lebḥeṛ n Yirikuk akk-d lebḥur, i d-yeddan yid-es waṭas n tabagust n yisaffen.
Nezger lebḥeṛ n igṭaṭ ( iɛedda) ɣer tmurt n Fluyas ; ma yella wamek, a nṛuḥ qṛib ad awḍen ɣer rrif n temdint n Ṛuma.
walaɣ deg unejmaɛ-nni azgen deg-sen d wamek ara t-skecmen ɣef wusu-inek, txeṣṣart ɣef yiman-nsen akken ilaq. ?ef ddemma n imeslayen-agi i gețmeslayeḍ-ed akka, a d-isbeggen belli anagar wid i d-yekkan si mkul tama, seg imawen-nsen tețxebbiṛem s ɣuṛ-ek.
Akken i t-nbecceṛ di tira iqedsen iqedsen n temdint n Gdeṛt-agi, i gețwaceggɛeḍ-ed ayen ur neṣfi ara, yessetḥa-iten di tigellilt yerna qṛib a d-yaweḍ wid i t-izedɣen di lexṣaṣ. Iberdan iɛewjen iwakken ad jemɛen, ɣeṛqent-id ɣer wemkan iqedsen, ibeḥṛiyen akk-d lebḥuṛ.
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen imednuben, yiwen kan qṛib a d-ffɣen seg wesɣaṛ ; ɛeṛden i k-d-tețmektayeḍ ɣuṛ-i iwakken ad țțujerden ayen akk i k-d-iṣaḥ ula d yiwen.
Ma d kečč m'ara tuẓumeḍ, ssired udem-ik, tdehneḍ aṣurdi n lfeṭṭa.
Ay atmaten, ayen akka i d-nniɣ fell-i akk-d lḥut s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ur yezmir ara a d-yekken si tmurt n Lud, d wid iteddun s ɣuṛ-sen ; lameɛna tbeddleḍ iman-ik ɣef ddemma n lis-agi, abeɛda wid yumnen yis.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Akaya, timura iqeṛben tamdint n Ludikus akk-d țelt n Arimati i d-yekker ɣer yemdanen. Ddant d lewḥuc iweɛṛen, tqebḥent s ujelkkaḍ ( s uqehheṛ ) i temdinin n tmurt n Akaya.
Timsalin-agi țelt n tmes i d-yețwaceggɛen aman i tlata wagguren si tmurt n Asya ibeɛden azal n tlatin n Frijt.
Lameɛna atan wayen yellan deg-ek ur iyi-neɛǧib ara : llan ɣuṛ-ek kra yemdanen mazal-iten ṭṭfen deg webrid n Lmasiḥ i gețmeslayeḍ ɣer tmurt n Yahuda yellan di tmurt n Asya. Ițɣawal-agi yenna-yas : « Mačči d lemtel i lɣaci-agi i k-d-iqqimen di temdint n Ifasus » ;
Mmekti-d ihi amek yezmer ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa, ma d wiyaḍ a ten-id-yerr ɣer webrid akk-d lweḥc, qṛib ad awḍen ɣer rrif n tmura nniḍen, ma d wid iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi.
